room_title: Escape room "The Work Place: Office Party" by Sprightly Escapes in Denver
room_description: The party planning committee at your regional paper supply company is throwing an office party. Unfortunately, the Assistant to the Regional Manager, Dwayne K. Schrumpf, has other plans. He has canceled the party in the name of office productivity. While Dwayne and  the boss are out on a sales call, you and your colleagues have 60 minutes to save the party.
